    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah i saw a note about the logging thing. but look closer at the dependency tree in the PR files. it basically moves away from the agentic runtime entirely in favor of stateless lambda functions. basically what do you think the long term impact is for the automation tasks you're currently handling?",
